        <h2 animate="title" data-w-id="2383073c-8e75-1350-8874-202f012b1a0f" style={{ opacity: 0, filter: 'blur(20px)' }} className="text-h2-8 no-margins low-height">Information Architecture<br /><br /><span className="text-span-417">We kicked off by exploring the space through a <strong>literature review</strong> and <strong>co-working sessions</strong> with stakeholders — uncovering <strong>real workflows</strong>, <strong>pain points</strong>, and <strong>process gaps</strong> directly from those navigating the system.</span></h2>
